[![](https://i1.wp.com/static.flickr.com/35/112586363_1bc628a218.jpg?w=960)](http://www.flickr.com/photos/adders/112586363/ "photo sharing") [Tunisian Shore, after the storm](http://www.flickr.com/photos/adders/112586363/), originally uploaded by [Adam Tinworth](http://www.flickr.com/people/adders/).
Another one from Tunisia at the end of last year, showing the strange accumulation of seaweed on the shore after a massive storm. Technorati Tags: [photos](http://www.technorati.com/tag/photos), [tunisia](http://www.technorati.com/tag/tunisia)
